        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="f_human_desc" value="Full expressive signal&lt;br&gt;available to LLM:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Tone, face, body&lt;br&gt;Physiology, history&lt;br&gt;Patterns over time&lt;br&gt;Unconscious signals&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&quot;Here's what I mean, how I&lt;br&gt;feel about it, and what&lt;br&gt;I'm not saying out loud&quot;&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=13;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
