        <mxCell id="f_llm_desc" value="Full intellectual capacity&lt;br&gt;available to human:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Reasoning, synthesis&lt;br&gt;Breadth, patience&lt;br&gt;Honest uncertainty signals&lt;br&gt;Persistent state over time&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&quot;Here's what I think, how&lt;br&gt;confident I am, and where&lt;br&gt;I'm guessing&quot;&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=13;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
